# Pre-sprint

## Approach
### DSL-Driven Evaluation

The platform uses a declarative DSL for:

- metrics
- pipelines
- thresholds
- runtime policies

This enables:
- reusable evaluation pipelines
- natural language pipeline generation
- planner-driven configuration

## Data models

### EvaluationInput
```json
{
  "text": "nullable string",

  "artifacts": [],

  "metadata": {}
}
```

### Artifact
```json
{
    "id": "UUIDv7 string",

    "modality": "pdf | image | text",

    "uri": "URI string",

    "mime_type": "nullable MIME type string",

    "extracted_text": "nullable string",

    "metadata": {}
}
```

### RuntimeEvent
```json
{
  "id": "UUIDv7",

  "timestamp": "ISO-8601 datetime string",

  "type": "component.started | component.completed | component.failed",

  "data": {},

  "metadata": {}
}
```

